Recommends: librsvg2-bin
Description: Read-only viewer for Microsoft Visio files
 VSDView is a read-only viewer for Microsoft Visio files (.vsdx and .vsd),
 built with GTK4 and libadwaita. It uses libvisio-ng for native Visio file
 parsing with support for both modern XML and legacy binary formats.
 .
 Features include interactive zoom, pan/drag navigation, shape info panel,
 shape tree sidebar, measurement tool, minimap, SVG export, layer
 visibility toggles, clickable hyperlinks, and search.
